<h4 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Duplicatetaskcreationissue"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);">Duplicate task creation issue</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Due to diff-2 idempotency layer f=
or incident creation, it's possible for duplication incident &amp; task cre=
ation for same entity</span></li>
<li><span>Raise it to <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:crmoncall@m=
yntra.com" style=3D"text-decoration: none;" rel=3D"nofollow">crmoncall@mynt=
ra.com</a></span></li>
</ul>
