olor: rgb(23,43,77);">Old refund details required</span></span></h4>
<ul>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Need to check if PPS Id is =
shared</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Need to login into myntra_c=
rm db and access imps_log table.</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">search with pps_id from the=
 column idempotrntId and get URN from urnno column</span></span></li>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Login into RNarchive DB and=
 search for data in Co$IMPS_SP table with urnno(myntra_urn) column</span></=
span></li>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">check if imps_RRN,myntra_st=
atus and myntra_Action data is there.share these details in ticket.</span><=
/span></li>
<li><span><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">If still not clear raise it=
 to&nbsp;</span></span><span><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:crmo=
ncall@myntra.com" style=3D"text-decoration: none;" rel=3D"nofollow">crmonca=
ll@myntra.com</a></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Surveyor">Surveyor</h2>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Tasky">Tasky</h2>
<h4 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Download/Uploadstuck">Download / Upload stuck</h=
4>
<h5 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Download">Download</h5>
<ul>
<li>Issue with downloads will be because of MWS mostly, which will be follo=
wed up with the team with relevant <strong>jobId</strong>. (#mws-prod-issue=
 Slack channel)</li>
<li>Downloading one file at a time is only possible, so when a job is stuck=
, re-downloads can't be triggered.&nbsp;</li>
<li>To overcome this, config is maintained which can be changed to allow re=
-downloads after "x" minutes.</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Upload">Upload</h5>
<ul>
<li>Uploads can be triggered again when it is stuck.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-Reportnotdownloadable:NoDataerror">Report not do=
wnloadable : No Data error</h4>
<ul>
<li>This occurs due to the user not having permission to download the repor=
t.</li>
<li>Issue can be raised with ServiceDesk team, asking them to copy permissi=
ons of the user who is able to download the file to the one facing the issu=
e.</li>
<li>CRM team can also help in sharing the exact permissions required for th=
e report if it's needed.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"CRMIssuesRunbook-RequiredDatanotpresentinreport">Required Data no=
t present in report</h4>
<ul>
<li>Check if the data is configured in&nbsp;<strong>report_additional_info&=
nbsp;</strong>table <strong>field_map</strong> column of <strong>myntra_tha=
nos&nbsp;</strong>DB. If not, add necessary data in the config.</li>
<li>If config is present, enrichment is not happening from Thanos, which ne=
eds to be checked with product / debugged further.</li>
</ul>
